n{{Avicii}}\n{{Robbie Williams singles}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Days}}\n[[Category:Avicii songs]]\n[[Category:2014 songs]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Avicii]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Brandon Flowers]]\n[[Category:Number-one singles in Finland]]\n[[Category:Number-one singles in Norway]]\n[[Category:Number-one singles in Sweden]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Vincent Pontare]]\n[[Category:Songs written by Salem Al Fakir]]\n[[Category:Song recordings produced by Vincent Pontare]]\n[[Category:Song recordings produced by Salem Al Fakir]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|2014 single by Avicii}}\n{{Infobox song\n| name       = The Days\n| cover      = The Days cover.png\n| alt        =\n| type       = single\n| artist     = [[Avicii]]\n| EP         = [[The Days / Nights EP]]\n| released   = {{Start date|2014|10|03|df=yes}}\n| format     = {{hlist|[[CD single|CD]]|[[Music download|digital download]]}}\n| recorded   = 2014\n| studio     =\n| venue      =\n| genre      = {{hlist|[[Folktronica]]|[[Soul music|soul]]|[[House music|house]]|[[Electronic dance music|EDM]]}}\n| length     = {{ubl|4:38 {{small|(album version)}}|3:45 {{small|(radio edit)}}|5:51 {{small|(extended mix)}}}}\n| label      = {{hlist|PRMD|[[Universal Music Group|Universal]]}}\n| writer     = {{hlist|[[Brandon Flowers]]|[[Salem Al Fakir]]|[[Avicii|Tim Bergling]]|[[Robbie Williams]]|[[Vincent Pontare]]}}\n| producer   = {{hlist|Salem Al Fakir|Avicii|Vincent Pontare}}\n| chronology = [[Avicii]]\n| prev_title = [[Dar um Jeito (We Will Find a Way)]]\n| prev_year  = 2014\n| next_title = [[Divine Sorrow]]\n| next_year  = 2014\n| misc       = {{Extra chronology\n | artist     = [[Robbie Williams]]\n | type       = singles\n | prev_title = [[Shine My Shoes]]\n | prev_year  = 2014\n | title      = The Days\n | year       = 2014\n | next_title = [[Party Like a Russian]]\n | next_year  = 2016\n}}\n{{External music video|{{YouTube|JDglMK9sgIQ| \"The Days\" (lyrics video)}} }}\n}}\n\n\"'''The Days'''\" is a song by Swedish DJ and record producer [[Avicii]], with vocals by English singer [[Robbie Williams]]. The song was written by [[Brandon Flowers]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nme.com/news/music/brandon-flowers-12-1209441|title=Brandon Flowers collaborates with Avicii for new version of \u2018The Days\u2019|website=nme.com}}</ref> [[Robbie Williams]], [[Salem Al Fakir]], Avicii and [[Vincent Pontare]],<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ascap.com/aceclient/AceClient/#ace/work/887518508|title=IBM Security Access Manager|website=mobile.ascap.com}}</ref> and was produced by Avicii, Fakir and Pontare. The song was played for the first time in [[Boston]], with uncredited vocals by Fakir. The song was released worldwide on 3 October 2014. It was released alongside \"[[The Nights]]\" in ''[[The Days / Nights EP]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/the-days-nights-ep/id943278970|title=The Days/Nights - EP by Avicii|date=1 January 2014|publisher=iTunes}}</ref> A planned release in the United Kingdom on 23 November 2014 was cancelled.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.fuse.tv/2014/10/avicii-the-days-robbie-williams|title=Avicii Returns With Genre-Defying \"The Days\" ft. U.K. Superstar Robbie Williams|last=Benjamin|first=Jeff|date=3 October 2014|publisher=fuse.tv}}</ref>\n\n==Composition==\n\"The Days\" is written in the key of C major, at a tempo of 127 BPM.<ref>[http://www.musicnotes.com/sheetmusic/mtd.asp?ppn=MN0140524 Avicii \"The Days\" Sheet Music] musicnotes.com</ref> The chord structure is based on the pop punk chord progression.\n\n==Recording==\nThe song was originally written with Vincent Pontare and Salem Al Fakir, but was meant to be a collaboration between [[Brandon Flowers]] and Avicii, with Flowers providing the vocals. However, due to Flowers' dissatisfaction with the recording, Avicii brought on a different vocalist, Robbie Williams.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/news/dance/6590204/avicii-brandon-flowers-days-killers|title=Hear Avicii's Awesome Unreleased Jam With the Killers' Brandon Flowers|website=billboard.com}}</ref>\n\n==Music video==\nAn official lyric video was also released on [[YouTube]] by the official Avicii [[Vevo]] channel.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JDglMK9sgIQ|title=Avicii - The Days (Lyric Video)}}</ref> In the video, an artist (later confirmed as [[INO (artist)|INO]]),<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ino.net|title=INO - Official artist website}}</ref> [[Spray painting|spray-paint]]s the lyrics of \"The Days\" in black against a white wall. Near the end of the video, a pan-out reveals the lyrics creating a portrait of Avicii, which is subsequently covered with splashes of coloured paint by the artist.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/code/6273847/avicii-the-days-lyric-video-exclusive|title=''Billboard'' magazine: Watch Avicii's 'The Days' Lyric Video|date=3 October 2014|work=Billboard}}</ref>\n\nAs of May 2018, the lyric video has been viewed more than 150 million times.<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=JDglMK9sgIQ|title=Avicii - The Days (Lyric Video)}}</ref>\n\n==Track listing==\n{{Track listing\n| headline = Digital download<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/au/album/the-days-single/id922528476|title=The Days - Single by Avicii on Apple Music|website=iTunes|language=en|access-date=2017-02-09}}</ref>\n| title1 = The Days\n| length1 = 4:38\n}}\n\n{{Track listing\n| collapsed = yes\n| headline = CD single<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.universal-music.de/main?url=L2F2aWNpaS9kaXNrb2dyYWZpZS9kZXRhaWwvcHJvZHVjdDoyMjE1ODcvdGhlLWRheXM=&album=221587|title=Universal Music Deutschland: Deine Stars, deine Musik, alle Genres - Universal Music|publisher=}}</ref>\n| title1 = The Days\n| note1 = Radio Edit\n| length1 = 3:45\n| title2 = The Days\n| note2 = Original Mix\n| length2 = 4:38\n| title3 = The Days\n| note3 = Extended Mix\n| length3 = 5:51\n| total_length = 14:14\n}}\n\n==Credits and personnel==\n*[[Brandon Flowers]] \u2013 lyrics, vocals {{small|(demo version only)}} <ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.discogs.com/Avicii-The-Days/release/6201108|title=Avicii - The Days|website=discogs.com}}</ref>\n*[[Salem Al Fakir]] \u2013 producer, vocals {{small|(demo version only)}}\n*[[Avicii|Tim Bergling]] \u2013 music, producer\n*[[Vincent Pontare]] \u2013 producer\n*[[Robbie Williams]] \u2013 vocals\n*Stuart Hawkes \u2013 mastering\n*Ash Pournouri \u2013 executive producer<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.discogs.com/Avicii-The-Days-Nights-EP/release/6369045|title=Avicii - The Days / Nights EP|website=Discogs}}</ref>\n\nCredits adapted from [[CD single]].<ref name=\"credits\">{{cite AV media notes|others=[[Avicii]]|title=The Days|year=2014|type=booklet|publisher=[[Universal Music Group|PM:AM Recordings]]|id=0602547072924}}</ref>\n\n==Charts and certifications==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\"\n|-\n! Chart (2014\u201315)\n! Peak<br />position\n|-\n{{singlechart|Australia|10|artist=Avicii|song=The Days|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"| Australia Dance ([[ARIA Charts|ARIA]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://pandora.nla.gov.au/pan/23790/20141022-0924/Issue1286.pdf|title=Week Commencing ~ 20 October 2014 ~ Issue #1286|work=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|publisher=[[Pandora Archive]]|date=20 October 2014|accessdate=5 November 2014}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|2\n|-\n{{singlechart|Austria|3|artist=Avicii|song=The Days|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Flanders Tip|2|artist=Avicii|song=The Days|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Flanders Dance|9|artist = Avicii|song = The Days|rowheader=true|accessdate=21 November 2014|refname=\"Flanders\"}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Wallonia Tip|2|artist=Avicii|song=The Days|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{singlechart|Wallonia Dance|11|artist = Avicii|song = The Days|rowheader=true|accessdate=7 November 2014|refname=\"Wallonia\"}}\n|-\n!scope=\"row\"|Brazil ([[Brasil Hot 100 